## Choose a sorting algorithm 
Supported sorting algorithms :  
- Selection sort
- Bubble sort
- Insertion sort

## Example usage
```
const sort = require('sorting-algorithm');

const arr = [1,9,2,8,3,7,4,7,5,6]
console.log(sort.insertionSort(arr))

// output: Took approximately n to sort
//         [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9]
```
